# MadSpin cascade for chargino+neutralino associated production (WN_HyyN).
# Placeholders (SEED_PLACEHOLDER, EVENTS_PLACEHOLDER) are filled per chunk
# by the Madgraph task before MadSpin is launched. x1->W n1 and n2->h01 n1
# are tree-level MSSM decays; W and h01 are left for Pythia (h01->yy filter).
set spinmode madspin
set seed SEED_PLACEHOLDER
import EVENTS_PLACEHOLDER
decay x1+ > w+ n1
decay x1- > w- n1
decay n2 > h01 n1
launch
